Steps:

Go to AWS Console → EC2 → Auto Scaling Groups
Create a Launch Template:
AMI
Instance type
Security group
Key pair
Click Create Auto Scaling Group
Configure:
Select VPC & subnets
Attach Load Balancer (optional but recommended)
Set:
Desired capacity
Min & Max instances
Add Scaling Policy:
Example: Add instance if CPU > 70%
Enable Health Checks
Review and create
